Attend Online and Learn 
-------------
At SOA Summit, top experts will discuss how a standards-based 'next-gen SOA' is already offering CIOs, Enterprise Architects, integration professionals fast, cost-effective and secure ways to deliver API, cloud and mobile success for their company's business. 

Topics will span architecture design, deployment and operations and will include:

* How SOA meets CIO needs for APIs, cloud, mobile, SaaS integration

* Leverage legacy resources (apps, data and security) for 'Edge of Enterprise' success

* F1000s tips to safely open APIs to outside developers, partners.

* Build in mobile success with SOA and new lightweight IT

* Extend and federate current SSO, Security and Compliance assets

* Detailed use cases and customer case studies

